						<h2>AML Audits</h2>
						<p>Mallon &amp; Johnson conducts independent testing of a firm’s AML program. Barbara Mallon and examiners conducting the independent testing are Certified Anti-Money Laundering Specialists<sup>&reg;</sup>. Generally, our testing will encompass the following:</p>
