							<li>AML Officer's role;</li>
							<li>AML Written Procedures</li>
							<li>Customer identification procedures;</li>
							<li>Beneficial owners and control person identification;</li>
							<li>Customer verification procedures;</li>
							<li>Cashiering procedures;</li>
							<li>Wire transfers;</li>
							<li>Detection and reporting of suspicious activities;</li>
							<li>OFAC checks;</li>
							<li>Training of Employees concerning AML; and</li>
							<li>314(a) and (b) requests.</li>
						</ul>
